description: Opaque identifier for a single video feed or multicast stream.
Operational theater: Continental US, Pacific, Europe, Middle East, Africa, Arctic.
Nominal frame rate of the feed in frames per second.
Compression format used for the stream.
Whether the transport or at-rest stream is encrypted.
Estimated end-to-end latency from sensor to consumer, in milliseconds.
Primary analytics/detector model applied to the feed.
Flag indicating the feed passed civilian-safety filtering policies.
